h2 View
.img.img_big.img_docs-project_view
p At the project page are view the current state of the project - name, description, collaborators and a limited list of project modules.
p A project owner has a green border in the collaboration list.
p You can edit the project via "Edit project" button at the secondary menu on the right. 


h1 Modules

h2 Create
p Each project can have modules. You can create a new one at Project page.
.img.img_big.img_docs-module_create
ul 
   li Name - unique name per project
   li Description - short description of the module
   li Dependency
      ul 
         li Independent - text
         li Package - based on some package (not implemented yet)
   li Type - change it if you want to use markdown, HTML, etc. tags
   li Text - module content


h2 View & Export
.img.img_big.img_docs-module_view

p Modules may import another module, e.g.:
code.
   This module have another module inside - ";;;module-name;;;" is replaced by module-name content.

p A result of an export:
code This module have another module inside - "This module uses <b>BOLD</b> text." is replaced by module-name content.

